  <brief_title>Effect of Vascular Inflow Occlusion in Open Liver Resection for Hepatocellular Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open Liver Resection With or Without Vascular Inflow Occlusion for Hepatocellular Carcinoma: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
